$ Bash: scripts

{ Count arguments

  The number of arguments with which a script was called is stored in `$#`.

  gh|about-Bash|/scripts/count-arguments||

}
{ Name of the script

  `$0` stores the name of the script.

  gh|about-Bash|/scripts/scriptname-in-dollar-0||

}

